Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}为什么一直要追我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}到底是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.33,0:01:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}那孩子很有素质吧 次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不过他的力量还没露出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你看怎样 要试他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.48,0:02:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}试他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.61,0:02:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}就挑学校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}是谁在攻击我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.82,0:02:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}城市为何变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}难道 刚才我看到的的女孩是幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}片名：夜来了(1)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}叶村凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我有事跟你谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}夜里七点在第二校舍屋顶见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}等一下 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你们的目的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}别动粗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}这么任性 是她拜托你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不好意思 叶村凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我们只是试一下你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}力量？什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}昨天 你避开交通标志时的敏锐直觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}还有避开我的攻击的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你是不知不觉中 使用“力量”的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}跟我们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}昨天...是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}等等 你们在闹什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}快把人带过来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你是叶村凉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我是天文部部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}小仓泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.73,0:05:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}拜托你 跟我们一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}他们...到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}那个...我不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你说你们是天文部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}而那只是 用来满混世人耳目的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}其实 你们是叫做“火蛇”的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}从蓝色月亮过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}在对抗昨天攻击我的怪物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.71,0:06:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}了不起 马上理解部长讲的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}这种人头次遇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我很不会解释的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}叶村 再来喝一杯茶如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.06,0:06:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}总之发生太多事了 我有点摸不着头绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}让我考虑一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}叶村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}今天很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}可否 请你在一星期内给我答覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.68,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}如果你不想 跟今天谈论的事物扯上关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.42,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}到时我们就会消除你的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}消除记忆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}吵死了 笨女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}别这样不要在意她就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}可是你不觉得发毛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}真拿您这个人没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}她出了点事 所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}破坏掉算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}雨好烦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}最近公园有个女色狼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}讨厌 你别老是在网上混了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.52,0:08:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}那是我们班的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}后藤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}叶村 我是小仓泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}前几天提的事你考虑过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.17,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}呃...我还没做好决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}今夜请到公园来好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.99,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我想让你看看 敌人是什么样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}后藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}学长...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}学长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}学长...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}两三天前 她就每夜到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}那是HIKARI的作法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}HIKARI 会嗅出人类不满足的欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}利用那个做能源来活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不赶快把HIKARI除去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}她将永远做梦下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}一直衰弱 知道死为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.96,0:11:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}拜托 与我们一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.04,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}可是怎样做才能对抗那怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}想使用“力量”是需要修行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}今天就一起试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}远古时代的火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.79,0:11:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}将无垢之血化为风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}赐你的力量给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}后藤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}凉 这边追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}破邪之刀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}小仓泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}凉 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}小仓泉 小仓泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}小仓泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}幸好赶上了 次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}好像没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}谢谢你 京华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}我看 这附近忽然传出不好的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}所以就赶来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}怎样 这样你相信我们的话了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}拜托 与我们一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}知道了 我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}古时的火焰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}给这个人治愈的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}这样... 她的痛苦的记忆就会消失吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}不知道 但我们也只能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}所以现在本地发生的 连续纵火事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}完全找不出动机呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}原因不明的可疑失火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}游戏中心失火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}百货公司失火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}精品店完全烧毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}你想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.51,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}就算这些事件是HIKARI干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.32,0:14:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fnKaiTi\b1}他们也不过是附着在 人类的欲望上来行动
